categories: Category:Articles that are known by a nickname

nodes.text: "Killer" was the nickname of a clone trooper pilot who served with High Jedi General Obi-Wan Kenobi's fleet during the Clone Wars.
Killer flew a clone Z-95 starfighter when General Grievous launched an assault on Obi-Wan Kenobi's fleet, but he was killed when his starfighter was shot down by droid starfighters.
